    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/9866d468f4b3186e8b2f04853e37bd81.webp?t=1768513002\" width=372 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《金银归家路 - Ten Thousand Coins: The Golden Merchant》</strong> 是一款剧情丰富的策略游戏，玩家将扮演一只深陷背叛与阴谋的小狐狸商人。你将踏上一段充满挑战的神奇冒险，躲避强大敌人的追捕，同时通过贸易活动不断积累财富，并沿途结交盟友，直至找到归途，寻回族人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/95b5dfe506344ac354d094ef2fe0a5ce.poster.avif?t=1768513002\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/95b5dfe506344ac354d094ef2fe0a5ce.webm?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/95b5dfe506344ac354d094ef2fe0a5ce.mp4?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时光倒流至十年前，在这片战火吞噬的土地上，一位来自瑞梵的商人意外揭开了一个惊人的秘密，并结识了一位神秘的小伙伴。他的每一个选择都将深深影响十年后众人的命运。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事与抉择</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸游戏之中，与角色一同踏上穿越两个时空线的深入探索之旅。见证你扮演的角色在跨时空的游戏世界中作出决策，而你的抉择将改变故事的走向。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/d866da26d2be9e9cbdf73c595cf0e0bd.poster.avif?t=1768513002\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/d866da26d2be9e9cbdf73c595cf0e0bd.webm?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/d866da26d2be9e9cbdf73c595cf0e0bd.mp4?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>以情动人，驰骋贸易之路</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情享受回合制交易的乐趣，自由支配时间与资源，与各路商人打交道时，记得要留意他们的情感与需求。了解商人们的喜好和需求是成功的关键，只有将这一切了然于心，你才能把握最佳时机。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/a33bc28102a85d4c7feba56d62f6c50b.poster.avif?t=1768513002\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/a33bc28102a85d4c7feba56d62f6c50b.webm?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/a33bc28102a85d4c7feba56d62f6c50b.mp4?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>商人之战 </strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途中，你必须时刻保持警惕，因为土匪和野兽会一直在暗中注视着你的马车。在这款游戏中，你将体验到具备贸易元素的独特回合制战斗。当战斗爆发时，你的行囊中的商品可以立即变身为战斗利器，每一件商品都拥有独特的特殊效果。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/c367caad78aee206340ceb067a4fcc47.poster.avif?t=1768513002\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/c367caad78aee206340ceb067a4fcc47.webm?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/c367caad78aee206340ceb067a4fcc47.mp4?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，如果你想避免战斗，还可以通过谈判或恐吓来实现和平解决！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/2915ab20c748928b2fc3173e608252ba.webp?t=1768513002\" width=372 height=45 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>重建瑞梵，再现昔日风采</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中的公司玩法，你将体验RPG和肉鸽玩法，扮演一位神秘商人，致力于重建瑞梵公司，使这座建筑重现昔日的繁荣灿烂。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/507af793271e9b2eb96d608eb8e17156.poster.avif?t=1768513002\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/507af793271e9b2eb96d608eb8e17156.webm?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157900/extras/507af793271e9b2eb96d608eb8e17156.mp4?t=1768513002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事模式 - 沉浸式的故事情节在两条时间线中交织，个性鲜明的角色轮番登场。你在重要环节作出的关键决策，将影响这段旅程的结局。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公司玩法 - 扮演瑞梵公司背后的神秘商人，重建这座破旧建筑，使其恢复昔日的辉煌。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细致精美的手绘艺术风格，深受动漫文化影响的美术元素。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索色彩缤纷的角色、城市和定居点，展开探险、贸易和声望建设。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百种独特的商品可供发现、使用和交易。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣、招募各类守卫和旅行者，组建独属于你的商队，在旅途中成为你的左膀右臂。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >往来城镇贸易的路途上，荒野遍布随机事件，以及，难缠的敌人。 </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敬请关注我们并将<strong>《金银归家路》</strong>加入愿望单，感谢支持！</h2>",
